        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer129329731" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4274271048394399451">Dr. Brown&apos;s writing is enjoyable - I read this book when I was flying between Ontario and Alberta. Some of the insights provided are simply building blocks on other works. He has a masterful way of writing and explaining the simple concepts of human life. He offers many tasks that help the reader with his or her personal &quot;challenges&quot;. My favorite chapter in the book is &quot;The Unconditional State&quot;. It reminded me how I should be living my own life. Dr. Brown has is an instinctive writer. <br/><br/><br/></span>
