              <span id="reviewTextContainer474952891" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14479931305070515134">This book has a simple premise: The world is divided between two types of people, those who are afraid of living, waiting to live; and those who have a deep desire to live life to its fullest. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

